I just got a call
from Main Justice.

17:30.424 --> 17:32.885
The Deputy Attorney General
wants us to go to DC

17:32.885 --> 17:34.470
to discuss this case with him.

17:34.470 --> 17:37.723
‐ That's‐‐that's unusual
this early in the case.

17:37.723 --> 17:39.016
‐ I know.

17:39.016 --> 17:40.685
If I'm getting calls,
it must mean that someone

17:40.685 --> 17:43.688
with a lot of influence really
doesn't like what we're doing.

17:43.688 --> 17:45.898
‐ When does he wanna
meet with us?

17:45.898 --> 17:48.484
‐ In two weeks.

17:48.484 --> 17:50.236
You ever met James Comey
in person?

17:50.236 --> 17:52.029
‐ No.
What's he like?

17:52.029 --> 17:54.156
‐ He's very tall.

17:54.156 --> 17:55.491
I'm gonna need more
on this video

17:55.491 --> 17:58.828
if we're gonna keep
this case open, you got it?

17:58.828 --> 18:00.871
Find me something good.

