1:00:33.922 --> 1:00:37.175
♪ She's my baby ♪

1:00:37.175 --> 1:00:39.928
♪ Ain't that something? ♪

1:00:39.928 --> 1:00:41.555
♪ But I know ♪

1:00:41.555 --> 1:00:45.767
♪ She belong‐‐
she belongs to you ♪

1:00:45.767 --> 1:01:05.825
♪ ♪

